title: THE Steve Wilkos Show 06.11.08
description:
DID BEVERLY DO IT?:
 --------------------
    Beverly&#039;s 1-year-old baby girl has been sick all her life. Recently, while in the hospital for an unexplained illness, doctors discovered she was poisoned with Acetone and found needles in the baby&#039;s ear and mouth. After investigating the issues, the hospital believes it was Beverly who caused the baby harm, a claim Beverly and husband Billy deny. Billy refuses to believe his wife could hurt their child, but Steve&#039;s promised to reveal the truth, and the results are appalling.
